# Project agent skills

Skill roots are **relative to the repo**. They are **not** auto-loaded like global Cursor skills: **read the matching `SKILL.md` with the Read tool** when the task fits, then follow that skill.

## 1) Matt Pocock pack — **`.agents/skills/`**

Categories: `engineering/`, `productivity/`, `misc/`, `personal/`, `in-progress/`, `deprecated/`. See **`.agents/skills/README.md`**.

**First-time repo setup (optional):** if `CONTEXT.md`, `docs/adr/`, or triage labels are missing but the user wants those workflows, read and follow **`.agents/skills/engineering/setup-matt-pocock-skills/SKILL.md`**.

### 1b) When to read which skill (core)

| Situation | Read this file |
|-----------|----------------|
| Bug hunt, unclear failure, perf regression, “why does this happen?” | `.agents/skills/engineering/diagnose/SKILL.md` |
| Tests-first work, red–green–refactor, new behaviour covered by tests | `.agents/skills/engineering/tdd/SKILL.md` |
| Align on a change, sharpen domain language, `CONTEXT.md` / ADRs | `.agents/skills/engineering/grill-with-docs/SKILL.md` |
| Same alignment, not code-specific | `.agents/skills/productivity/grill-me/SKILL.md` |
| Turn conversation into a PRD (as defined in the skill) | `.agents/skills/engineering/to-prd/SKILL.md` |
| Split a plan/spec into issues | `.agents/skills/engineering/to-issues/SKILL.md` |
| Triage / label workflow for tickets | `.agents/skills/engineering/triage/SKILL.md` |
| Architecture / “ball of mud” deepening pass | `.agents/skills/engineering/improve-codebase-architecture/SKILL.md` |
| Explain unfamiliar code with system context | `.agents/skills/engineering/zoom-out/SKILL.md` |
| Throwaway prototype (CLI or UI variations) | `.agents/skills/engineering/prototype/SKILL.md` |
| Compact handoff for another agent | `.agents/skills/productivity/handoff/SKILL.md` |
| User asks for ultra-compressed replies | `.agents/skills/productivity/caveman/SKILL.md` |
| Authoring a new skill | `.agents/skills/productivity/write-a-skill/SKILL.md` |
| Husky / pre-commit / lint-staged setup | `.agents/skills/misc/setup-pre-commit/SKILL.md` |
| Migrate tests to @total-typescript/shoehorn | `.agents/skills/misc/migrate-to-shoehorn/SKILL.md` |
| Block dangerous git via hooks (Claude Code–oriented) | `.agents/skills/misc/git-guardrails-claude-code/SKILL.md` |
| Exercise / course scaffolding | `.agents/skills/misc/scaffold-exercises/SKILL.md` |

### 1c) Personal, in-progress, deprecated (use when the user asks)

| Situation | Read this file |
|-----------|----------------|
| Obsidian vault workflows | `.agents/skills/personal/obsidian-vault/SKILL.md` |
